snippet.title: Yume Nikki Fangame playthrough - The Door of Thoughts
snippet.description:
Content warning:
- Blood, gore, and violence
- Depiction of suicide and suicidal ideation
- Loud noises and loud music
- Jumpscares
- Bright colors and flashing lights

Read more about this fangame: https://ynfg.yume.wiki/The_Door_Of_Thoughts
Download: http://www.mediafire.com/download/xd2mlcl6mhe25br/Project1.rar

TIMESTAMPS:
0:00 Starting the game, getting Pinch ITEM from dream bed
0:53 Getting Joinks and Fast EFFECTS, Seeing Uninvited Party EVENT
4:19 Trying on Menu Types, Seeing Nailed Michi EVENT
7:05 Getting Sword EFFECT, Seeing Dancing Laughter EVENT, Getting Uboa EFFECT
12:01 Getting Cloud, Onryo and Headless EFFECTS
16:11 Seeing Tonome EVENT, Failed attempt at seeing Bizarre Bird event
19:39 Reading screens at the Library, Seeing CONFUSED Picture EVENT
21:20 Getting Lampie and Opposites EFFECTS, Seeing Prankster and Tokone's Room EVENTS
24:29 Seeing Stabbing Sword EVENT
26:07 Using the Lampie Effect's action
26:30 Dropping off all Effects, Seeing ENDING
